bio.openEndedText: Excellent service, reliability, dependability - words I go by to provide you the best trip experience. My name is Jay, and thank you for choosing one of my vehicles for your next adventure.

Welcome to my personal collection of cars. I am one of the highest rated and top hosts for the Palm Springs area. With over 1000+ trips completed, you can start your trip with confidence, knowing you are being serviced by a professional. I have several different style cars available. Please scroll down to see my list of cars.
*I strive to accommodate you. If you have a request, please send me a message. [Number redacted for privacy and security]
*Car is always delivered with a full tank of gas
*All cars are checked and cleaned before hand-off. 
I look forward to serving you when you visit the Palm Springs area.
Thank you, Tom
Love cars and take good care of them. Thank you for your interest in my Nissan Titan.

Jax Worx for you around the clock! Jackson and Andrea Parents of 3, Prioritizing building our turo business and transportation company from home. I’m always available for last minute bookings midnight bookings and we can get you a car any time you need it! 
I will be glad to get a car ready for you or find you one that suits your needs any time of day! 
We strive for above and beyond customer care, car cleanliness and maintenance that you won’t find with most hosts. 
We are dedicated to my be on time clean and gassed up and our reviews speak for themselves!
Thank you for looking into our cars and allowing us to serve you we look forward to serving you!

Hello, my name is Jeremy. I run this account with my Father Octavio. We have both lived in the desert all our lives. If you are visiting from out of town we recommend checking out Joshua tree national park, Gabino’s Crêperie in Palms Springs to eat, or if you feel like shopping around, the Cabazon Outlets are short drive away. Thank you for booking with us and we hope we cross Roads again. 

- Jeremy and Octavio

Exceptional cars should come with an exceptional host. I strive to be the best host you will ever have on Turo. I am always available to my guests 24/7 before and during your trip should you need to contact me. I am committed to making your Turo experience exceptional and your trip enjoyable!
Hello, my name is Jose. Been in the auto industry for 20+ years. Cars are my passion, I strive for perfection and satisfaction. Always looking for ways to make your experience as easy as possible.
